Class ProductionRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • Controller
      • ProductionRecord
  • public class ProductionRecord
extends Controller
    Represents a ProductionRecord that will be store in the database PRODUCTIONRECORD. A ProductionRecord have an name and id of the product, productionNumber, serialNumber and dateProduced.
